Definition: the fifth pillar of Islam is a pilgrimage to Mecca during the month of Dhu al-Hijja
Example: at least once in a lifetime a Muslim is expected to make a religious journey to Mecca and the Kaaba; for a Muslim the hajj is the ultimate act of worship
Synonyms: haj, hadj, pillar_of_Islam, noun, act, pilgrimage, the, fifth, pillar, of, Islam, is, a, to, Mecca, during, month, Dhu, al-Hijja, at, least, once, in, lifetime, Muslim, expected, make, religious, journey, and, Kaaba, for, ultimate, worship
Category: noun.cognition
